<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Home</title>

        <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/pngegg.png"/>


        <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.9.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-gH2yIJqKdNHPEq0n4Mqa/HGKIhSkIHeL5AyhkYV8i59U5AR6csBvApHHNl/vI1Bx" crossorigin="anonymous">


    </head>
    <body>

        <div class="container">
            <%- include('../partials/logo'); %>
            <div class="info text-center mt-4 mb-4">
                <span class="h5 text-muted">Cole a URL para ser encurtada</span>
            </div>
            
            
            <form action="/New" method="post" class="home-form d-flex justify-content-center">
                <input  type="text" name="url" placeholder="Cole o link aqui" required>
                <button id="post-url" class="btn btn-primary d-flex flex-row align-items-center" type="submit">Encurtar <i class="bi bi-link"></i></button>
            </form>

            <div class="home-info text-center mt-5">
                <p>O Encurtador de URL permite diminuir um link longo tornando-o fácil de lembrar</p>
                <p>Após encurtar a URL, é possível saber <a class="link" href="/clicks">quantos cliques ela recebeu</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <%-include("../partials/footer"); %>
        
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-A3rJD856KowSb7dwlZdYEkO39Gagi7vIsF0jrRAoQmDKKtQBHUuLZ9AsSv4jD4Xa" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    </body>
</html>